    <release version="49.0" date="2025-09-12">
      <description>
        <ul>
          <li>Added a simple highscoring system that tracks your personal best in each difficulty</li>
          <li>Added a lock button to the earmark picker to let you enter earmarks one at a time or multiple in one go</li>
