    <release version="47.0" date="2024-09-13">
      <description>
        <p>Gnome Sudoku 47 features:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access to 6 new customizations and 3 returning ones in the new Preferences window</li>
          <li>A new pencil button and shortcut to toggle earmark input</li>
          <li>Support for the new Gnome Shell 47 colors for both the selection and the highlighter</li>
          <li>Details for each accelerator in the new dedicated keyboard shortcuts window</li>
          <li>New zoom buttons and shortcuts to further adjust the size of numbers</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
